{"tid":922800,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"更新左隻自製Sticker既 app","createTime":"2018-11-30T16:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T05:45:11.000Z","uid":30117,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"727c502824a645eb37c7ba90d0643f709294afd8","tid":922800,"uid":30117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T16:20:49.000Z","msg":"大家想整自己既Sticker 可以用下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多謝各位巴打絲呢一個星期既支持<br />\n經過左咁多日, 不停改進同增加唔同既功能, 終於黎到2.0既更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nWSTicK既宗旨係希望各位巴打絲用落可以以最簡單既方法整自己既Stickers<br />\n今次更新最主要係加入退地同crop圖功能, 優化同修正唔同既問題, UI上都改左好多希望各位睇落會舒服啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今後亦都會繼續加入唔同既功能同優化<br />\n一個人既力量真係好細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，有你地既支持同幫忙WSTicK 會愈黎愈好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/wstick/id1442273161?mt=8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2Fwstick%2Fid1442273161%3Fmt%3D8&d=eIpUEpxYKT4anwe6ErL8sUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=237c24a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/hk/app/wstick/id1442273161?mt=8</a><br />\n<br />\n大家如果有咩問題可以去Facebook 同IG page 講底, 我地一定會決解<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nfacebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WSTicKHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWSTicKHK%2F&d=eIpUEpxYKT4anwe6ErL8sUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=48575887\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WSTicKHK/</a><br />\ninstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/wstick.j/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fwstick.j%2F&d=eIpUEpxYKT4anwe6ErL8sUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=808ab8b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/wstick.j/</a>"},{"pid":"b8