新圖(e.g c)個陣個次序就會係a(第一張),b(第二張),d(第三張),c(第四張圖),如果可以做到比人改埋個sticker次序就更好喇,即係由a,b,d,c -&gt; a,b,c,d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T07:11:51.000Z","msg":"多謝打巴既支持同建議，呢個功能我地已經諗到點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為今個版本主要改退地crop 圖同修正啲bug, 我地會係黎緊既更新加入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77cdeec413149aa29606b3a24e8c6d3d04474149","tid":922800,"uid":51411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T07:16:00.000Z","msg":"以前用巴打個apps整左兩set送比人<br />\n感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e98ab4f6374fa73bad6e8ae520cfba5ff4831611","tid":922800,"uid":30117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T09:20:45.000Z","msg":"! 各位分享唔到既巴絲打，請檢查貼紙包入面有冇&rdquo;/&ldquo;呢個符號，如果有呢個符號可能要請大家刪除呢個字😭🙏🏻 <br />\n<br />\n事源有朋友發現分享唔到新加既sticker, 經過查證原來Sticker 既名稱暫時唔可以有 &rdquo;/&ldquo; 既存在，我地會想辦法可否解決😱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sLg333d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsLg333d.png&h=b481c1ff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81179eb4ae6938228173ecb92e837d726cf25eeb","tid":922800,"uid":197732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T09:55:34.000Z","msg":"終於有退地啦喎！ <br />\n個退地fuction 比eraser 好用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nching 加油 有冇phase 3 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320c3e9a43158d261099f6aa0054a3929a686677","tid":922800,"uid":30117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"81179eb4ae6938228173ecb92e837d726cf25eeb","tid":922800,"uid":197732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T09:55:34.000Z","msg":"終於有退地啦喎！ <br />\n個退地fuction 比eraser 好用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nc